cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV. 

The paper is about a reinforcement learning algorithm, which is a subfield of machine learning. Specifically, it focuses on adapting the Soft Actor-Critic algorithm for discrete action settings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The algorithm may also have applications in control systems (cs.SY) and computer vision (cs.CV) domains, but these are less likely.
